[30;1m87670 | [0m[35m    // It returns true if ',' is found, false otherwise. If anything other than ',' or '}' is found,[0m
[30;1m87671 | [0m[35m    // then we are in error and we abort.[0m
[30;1m87672 | [0m[35m    if ((error = has_next_field().get(has_value) )) { abandon(); return error; }[0m

[30;1m87675 | [0m[35m  // If the loop ended, we're out of fields to look at.[0m
